trans-unit.source: Represents a <xref href="System.Printing.PrintJobPriority"></xref> property (and its value) of a printing system hardware or software component.
trans-unit.target: Representerar en <xref href="System.Printing.PrintJobPriority"> </xref> egenskap (och dess värde) för en utskrift maskinvaru- eller systemkomponent.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintJobPriorityProperty"></xref> class for the specified property.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintJobPriorityProperty"> </xref> klass för den angivna egenskapen.

trans-unit.source: The `attributeName` should be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular <xref:System.Printing.PrintJobPriority> property of a print system object, including casing.
trans-unit.target: Den `attributeName` ska skrivas exakt samma som namnet på en viss <xref:System.Printing.PrintJobPriority>-egenskapen för ett utskriftssystem objekt, inklusive versaler och gemener.</xref:System.Printing.PrintJobPriority>

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Priority%2A> property of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo> object must be spelled "Priority", not "JobPriority".
trans-unit.target: Till exempel den <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Priority%2A>egenskapen för en <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo>objektet stavat "Prioritet", inte "JobPriority".</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo> </xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Priority%2A>

trans-unit.source: The name of the <xref href="System.Printing.PrintJobPriority"></xref> property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintJobPriorityProperty"></xref> represents.
trans-unit.target: Namnet på den <xref href="System.Printing.PrintJobPriority"> </xref> egenskap som den <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintJobPriorityProperty"> </xref> representerar.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintJobPriorityProperty"></xref> class that has the specified value for the specified attribute.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintJobPriorityProperty"> </xref> klass som har det angivna värdet för det angivna attributet.

trans-unit.source: The `attributeName` should be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular <xref:System.Printing.PrintJobPriority> property of a print system object, including casing.
trans-unit.target: Den `attributeName` ska skrivas exakt samma som namnet på en viss <xref:System.Printing.PrintJobPriority>-egenskapen för ett utskriftssystem objekt, inklusive versaler och gemener.</xref:System.Printing.PrintJobPriority>

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Priority%2A> property of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo> object must be spelled "Priority", not "JobPriority".
trans-unit.target: Till exempel den <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Priority%2A>egenskapen för en <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo>objektet stavat "Prioritet", inte "JobPriority".</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo> </xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Priority%2A>

trans-unit.source: The name of the <xref href="System.Printing.PrintJobPriority"></xref> property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintJobPriorityProperty"></xref> represents.
trans-unit.target: Namnet på den <xref href="System.Printing.PrintJobPriority"> </xref> egenskap som den <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintJobPriorityProperty"> </xref> representerar.

trans-unit.source: The value of the property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintJobPriorityProperty"></xref> represents.
trans-unit.target: Värdet på egenskapen som den <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintJobPriorityProperty"> </xref> representerar.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the value of the property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintJobPriorityProperty"></xref> represents.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger värdet på egenskapen som den <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintJobPriorityProperty"> </xref> representerar.
